episodes.title: I tried food made by a cult
episodes.description:
I visit the infamous Yellow Deli in Kingston Ontario Canada to try their food. It was definitely an experience I'll never forget.

**Disclaimer: This video was made for comedic purposes and to shed some light on the Yellow Deli but I strongly encourage you to read through its controversial history, definitely worth a read**

0:00 Intro
0:45 Spinwich
2:12 Reuben
4:34 Mango Mate
6:04 Carrot Cake
